==English==
=== Etymology ===
Latin '''[[gloria]]'''
===Noun===
'''glory''' (''plural'' glories)

# Great beauty or [[splendour]], of such [[overwhelmingness]] that it is considered powerful.
# [[honour|Honour]] and [[valour]].
# Worship, praise, as in ''glory to God''.

